  "prompt": "Xavier school of human resource?",
  "response": "Xavier School of Human Resource Management (XAHR) is a prestigious institution located in India, specifically in Jamshedpur, Jharkhand. It is part of Xavier University and is known for its rigorous academic programs focused on human resource management and related fields. The school offers various programs, including a Master's in Human Resource Management (MHRM) and other specialized courses aimed at developing skills necessary for effective human resource management in organizations.\n\nXAHR emphasizes a holistic approach to HR education, incorporating both theoretical knowledge and practical application. The curriculum typically covers various aspects of human resource management, including talent acquisition, organizational behavior, labor laws, performance management, and strategic HR.\n\nThe school is also renowned for its placement records and industry connections, providing students with opportunities to engage with professionals and companies in the HR field. If you're seeking further information about specific programs, admission criteria, or campus life at XAHR, I recommend checking their official website or contacting the institution directly.",
